&lt;p data-start=&quot;0&quot; data-end=&quot;348&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(59, 60, 54);&quot;&gt;True Classic is looking for an &lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(75, 75, 105);&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;AI Engineer&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt; to design, build, and deploy AI-powered applications and workflows that solve real business problems across the company. In this hands-on, execution-focused role, you will work cross-functionally to integrate AI into how we acquire customers, maximize lifetime value, and streamline operations.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;350&quot; data-end=&quot;632&quot; data-is-last-node=&quot;&quot; data-is-only-node=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(59, 60, 54);&quot;&gt;You’ll thrive here if you’re a problem solver first—someone who would rather ship solutions than wait on specs or build slide decks. You’re comfortable writing clean, production-ready code, moving quickly, and turning ambiguous problems into real, working systems that drive impact.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(59, 60, 54);&quot;&gt;All True Classic roles are global and omni-channel, driving accountability across product categories, regions, and sales/marketing channels. This role will allow you to impact operations worldwide, ensuring alignment with our business objectives and delivering success across diverse markets and platforms.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
