&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(59, 60, 54);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(59, 60, 54);&quot;&gt;Own and drive the company’s highest-priority strategic and operational initiatives, serving as the quarterback responsible for clarity, momentum, and outcomes from start to finish&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(59, 60, 54);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(59, 60, 54);&quot;&gt;Translate ambiguous problems into structured workplans with clear success metrics&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(59, 60, 54);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(59, 60, 54);&quot;&gt;Drive execution across multiple teams, holding stakeholders accountable to timelines and results&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
