&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(59, 60, 54);&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Strategic Analysis &amp;amp; Business Problem-Solving&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(59, 60, 54);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(59, 60, 54);&quot;&gt;Apply a rigorous, first-principles approach to

